53:20.952 --> 53:23.011
Make some tea, buster.

54:14.038 --> 54:15.733
Why are you dressed?

54:19.176 --> 54:21.542
Because I think
you might be about to leave me...

54:21.612 --> 54:24.672
and I didn't want to be wearing
a dressing gown.

54:27.585 --> 54:29.917
I slept with someone in New York.

54:31.155 --> 54:32.486
A whore.

54:33.824 --> 54:35.121
I'm sorry.

54:39.497 --> 54:41.328
Why did you tell me?

54:42.266 --> 54:45.064
- I couldn't lie to you.
- Why not?

54:46.404 --> 54:48.065
Because I love you.

55:03.821 --> 55:05.152
It's fine.

55:06.023 --> 55:08.014
Really? Why?

55:13.097 --> 55:14.792
Something's wrong.

55:19.236 --> 55:20.567
Tell me.

55:24.075 --> 55:25.906
Are you leaving me?

55:30.314 --> 55:31.975
Because of this?

55:34.652 --> 55:35.812
Why?

55:37.922 --> 55:39.253
Dan.

55:41.325 --> 55:42.622
Cupid?

55:44.462 --> 55:46.054
He's our joke.

55:47.031 --> 55:48.362
I love him.

55:49.767 --> 55:51.701
You're seeing him now?

55:54.071 --> 55:55.663
Since when?

56:01.212 --> 56:04.045
Since my opening last year.

56:05.416 --> 56:06.974
I'm disgusting.

56:09.653 --> 56:11.245
You're phenomenal.

56:12.857 --> 56:14.518
You're so clever.

56:16.927 --> 56:18.690
Why did you marry me?

56:20.397 --> 56:22.888
