56:22.967 --> 56:25.959
- Why did you tell me you wanted children?
- Because I did.

56:26.036 --> 56:28.869
- And now you want children with him?
- Yes.

56:31.008 --> 56:32.566
I don't know.

56:36.080 --> 56:37.604
But we're happy...

56:38.816 --> 56:40.147
aren't we?

56:45.422 --> 56:48.084
