57:21.625 --> 57:23.616
Just answer the question.

57:23.861 --> 57:25.522
Is he good?

57:25.863 --> 57:27.194
Yes.

57:29.700 --> 57:31.292
Better than me?

57:31.635 --> 57:33.694
- Different.
- Better?

57:36.407 --> 57:38.739
- Gentler.
