57:53.891 --> 57:56.553
You're making the mistake of your life.

57:58.362 --> 58:01.854
You're leaving me because you believe
that you don't deserve happiness...

58:01.932 --> 58:03.524
but you do, Anna.

58:06.470 --> 58:09.496
Did you have a bath
because you had sex with him?

58:10.241 --> 58:12.368
So you wouldn't smell of him?

58:13.777 --> 58:15.938
So you'd feel less guilty?

58:17.114 --> 58:18.706
How do you feel?

58:19.383 --> 58:20.873
