58:22.353 --> 58:24.184
Did you ever love me?

58:25.055 --> 58:26.215
Yes.

58:58.822 --> 59:00.653
Did you do it here?

59:02.960 --> 59:04.120
No.

59:04.561 --> 59:05.892
Why not?

59:08.365 --> 59:10.128
Do you wish we did?

59:10.200 --> 59:11.997
Just tell me the truth.

59:13.904 --> 59:15.735
Yes, we did it here.

59:18.742 --> 59:19.902
Where?

59:24.948 --> 59:26.108
There.

59:28.652 --> 59:29.983
On this?

59:34.191 --> 59:36.489
We had our first fuck on this.

59:37.294 --> 59:38.989
Did you think of me?

59:41.832 --> 59:43.163
When?

59:46.236 --> 59:48.136
When did you do it here?

59:48.472 --> 59:50.997
- Answer the question!
- This evening.

59:55.813 --> 59:57.246
Did you come?

59:59.450 --> 01:00:02.510
- Why are you doing this?
- 'Cause I want to know.

01:00:03.687 --> 01:00:05.917
- Yes, I came.
- How many times?

01:00:05.989 --> 01:00:07.854
